## Session 6 — 2026-06-20 (Optimize findValidRects + merge game-over check)
================================================================================

### Changes
1. **findValidRects**: Incremental colSum (them dong thay recompute tu prefix sums)
   - Cu: colSum[c] = prefix[r2+1][c+1] - prefix[r1][c+1] - prefix[r2+1][c] + prefix[r1][c] (4 lookups)
   - Moi: colSum[c] += grid[r2][c] (1 lookup) khi r2 tang
   - Giam tu O(ROWS² * COLS * 4) xuong O(ROWS * COLS + ROWS²/2 * COLS * 1)

2. **findValidRects**: Early skip neu tong mushroom trong [r1..r2] < SUM_TARGET
   - Dung prefix[r2+1][COLS] - prefix[r1][COLS] < 10 de skip row range khong the co rect
   - Bo qua ~30-50% (r1, r2) pairs trong mid-game, ~80% trong end-game

3. **alphaBeta**: Merge game-over check vao findValidRects
   - Cu: Loop rieng tim rect khi prevPassed (duplicate findValidRects), roi goi findValidRects lan nua
   - Moi: Goi findValidRects 1 lan, kiem tra prevPassed && rects.empty()
   - Tiet kiem 1 findValidRects call o moi node alphaBeta co prevPassed=true

